{
  "stem": "22174.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in reality, it was a course to train people to smuggle in immigrants, to run the British blockade, because they didn't allow any Jewish immigration anymore.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so they had an organization that stretched all over Europe and they brought in refugees from the Nazi-occupied countries to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had to run the British blockade.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that course was to train people to work in that network.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so I went to a course also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had no work, so I went to the course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And at the end of the course, we had a practice run.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We emptied out a ship from fish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was hundreds of-- I don't know how many hundreds of refugees were on the ship.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I have a-- I made a drawing a couple of years ago from my memory [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] how we-- how that [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We took a ship in at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, we a little-- we had this lamp, a kerosene lamp, in the rocks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had-- there was a rocky coast.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In the rocks we had a lamp so the ship followed that light and came in as much-- as close to the coast as it could have.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then it dropped anchor and then we swim out-- no.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They sent one of the lifeboats.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we boarded that lifeboat and rowed back to the ship.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then we took them out of the lifeboats and filled them up with refugees.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I rowed one of the boats.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was so full, we couldn't-- there was no room in the boat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We put in as many people as we could.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I sat at the [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] front end of the boat and rowed.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
